---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service — troniti">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-24">
    <div class="mb-12 flex justify-center">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
        <span class="inline-block h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
        troniti
      </a>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-text-muted">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <div class="mt-12 space-y-8 text-text-muted">
      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>These terms govern your use of this website (troniti.com), the marketing site for troniti, a non-custodial TRON yield-management service. By accessing or using the site, you agree to be bound by these terms. If you do not agree, please do not use the site. Use of the troniti service itself is governed by a separate agreement presented at onboarding.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Use of Site</h2>
        <p>You may view this site and join the waitlist for informational purposes. You agree not to misuse the site, attempt to disrupt its operation, or use it in violation of applicable law.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">No Financial Advice</h2>
        <p>Content on this site is for general information only and is not financial, investment, or tax advice. Yield figures (including the ~15% combined figure) describe the operating model and historical on-chain results; they are illustrative and not a guarantee of future returns. Staking and on-chain activity carry risk.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Non-Custodial Service</h2>
        <p>troniti operates a restricted, on-chain TRON account permission and never takes custody of your funds or private keys. The permission cannot transfer or unstake your assets and is revocable by you at any time. You remain solely responsible for your wallet and keys.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content, design, and code on this site are the property of troniti. You may not copy, modify, or distribute any part of the site without permission.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>This site is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. To the maximum extent permitted by law, troniti is not liable for any damages arising from the use of this site.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Changes</h2>
        <p>We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-text">Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions? Reach us on X at <a href="https://x.com/ahmlvs" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-hover">@ahmlvs</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <a href="/" class="text-sm text-text-muted hover:text-text">&larr; Back to home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
